config_intro_text:
This report includes the results of the RNASeq analysis pipeline developed by the National Facility for Data 
Handling and Analysis based on the nf-core/rnaseq pipeline, with some modifications to suit our needs.
This pipeline performs quality control, alignment, quantification, and differential expression analysis of bulk
transcriptomics data.
config_report_comment: This report has been generated by the nfdata-omics/rnaseq analysis pipeline.
config_subtitle: National Facility for Data Handling and Analysis - Human Technopole
